Hope is a light that shines like the sun

00:54:48.468 --> 00:54:52.806 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As we see ourselves there

00:54:52.806 --> 00:54:58.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the new world to come.

00:55:03.850 --> 00:55:08.288 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And ev’ry word from His mouth

00:55:08.288 --> 00:55:12.826 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Will do all for which He sent it out.

00:55:12.826 --> 00:55:17.364 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah’s will for this earth is

00:55:17.364 --> 00:55:23.370 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Fulfilling ev’ry living things’ last wish.

